                    <span>Give it up folks--the book is on Boston's best-seller list.  It's a waste of time to bash Dan.  He loves getting readers riled up, doesn't care what you think of his writing nor his overlong ride the Curse money train--just as long as you keep his name circulating.  He loves being hated because it means you are paying attention. He truly cannot help that his mean-spirited bitterness about an unhappy personal life seep into his Red Sox coverage.  Just ignore him and he will go away eventually.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">What is Dan going to do now?</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
