                    <span>DAN IS A LOUSY WRITER WHO HAS MADE HIS ENTIRE CAREER DEPICTING THE NEVERENDING TORTURE OF BEING A RED SOX FAN AND PLAYER, ALWAYS BEING BRIDESMAIDS AND NEVER BRIDES BECAUSE THE BETTER TEAM, THE NEW YORK YANKEES WAS ALWAYS IN THEIR WAY. WHAT ARE YOU GOING TO DO NOW, DAN? OH, WRITE ABOUT HOW IT'S ALL OVER? HE ADDS NO POSSIBLE INSIGHT TO HISTORY, AS IT ALREADY HAPPENED AND PRETTY MUCH EVERYONE KNEW ABOUT IT. WHAT COULD HE POSSIBLY HAVE TOLD US? NOTHING, THAT'S WHAT. AND HE'S NOT EVEN A REAL FAN! WHAT A WASTE OF TIME!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The Curse of the Talentless Hack</div>
